## Install

[![https://nodei.co/npm/@airjam/table-view.png?downloads=true&downloadRank=true&stars=true](https://nodei.co/npm/@airjam/table-view.png?downloads=true&downloadRank=true&stars=true)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@airjam/table-view)

```shell
npm install @airjam/table-view
```

[Browser](https://airjam-co.github.io/table-view/dist/library.min.js)

```html
<script src="https://airjam-co.github.io/table-view/dist/library.min.js"></script>
```

## Import package to the project

### TypeScript

```typescript
import tableView from "@airjam/table-view";
```

### JavaScript

```javascript
var tableView = require("@airjam/table-view");
```

## package.json

- name
- description
- umdName
- libraryFile
- main

- homepage
- repository
- bugs
- keywords

- github_token

`npm run build`

`npm run watch`

`npm run test`
